revision.text:
{{nihongo|'''Mount Myōken'''|妙見山}} is the name of several mountains in [[Japan]].
* [[Mount Myōken (Nose)]] on the borders of Hyogo and Osaka prefectures.
* [[Mount Myōken (Tajima)]] in Hyogo Prefecture.
* [[Mount Myōken (Tokushima)]] in Tokushima Prefecture.
{{Mountainindex}}
{{disambig}}

